      "CareerPathAndProgression": {
        "Html": "\u003Cp\u003EIf you can show an agent you have potential they may put you forward for auditions and castings. Agents usually take a fee of about 10% to 25% from your earnings.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYou could take further training and move into directing, scriptwriting, drama therapy or teaching.\u003C/p\u003E"
